welcome_message_body: Welcome to Burnsville, a charming city known for its beautiful parks, vibrant arts scene, and friendly community. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Burnsville has to offer during your visit!

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The largest and busiest terminal at MSP, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal mainly used by low-cost carriers and regional airlines.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: A smaller terminal mainly used by Delta Air Lines.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Flying Cloud Airport serves both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Flying Cloud Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Downtown Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Downtown Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal of Anoka County–Blaine Airport, serving domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: A smaller terminal dedicated to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
